					"class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
					"markdown": "Compatible with iOS 7, 8, 9 and 10\n\nCompatible with R.Petrichâ€™s Activator.\n\nShould work with iPhones, iPods, iPads.\n\nSmartVolumeControl, the most Advanced Volume Controller for iOS, allows you to customise the native Volume HUD Window and choose between 8 different custom View Styles, including Android's Nougat-Like HUD, YouTube-Like Volume and WhatsApp Status Volume.\n\nIts highly customizable and it will allow you to change the default volume steps, the HUD auto dismiss time, control the volume from your lockscreen, costumize colors and the position of the View Styles, add shadow to them, present the volume with 15(!) Activator actions and set the volume level with your touches (forget about pressing volume up/down) and much more.\n\nConfigure options from settings."
